{
  "texts": [
    "For example, Ziems et al.",
    "evaluated LLMs from the GPT family and FLAN-T5 on multiple computational social science tasks such as toxicity detection and positive framing 7.",
    "These studies can involve either so-called \"zero-shot\" evaluations, where only unlabeled test data is provided for analysis or \"few-shot\" tests or \"fine-tuning\", where a sample of annotated data is provided for analysis prior to the presentation of test cases.",
    "In the health domain, most recent evaluations of LLMs focus on clinical data such as clinical notes, Electronic Health Records (EHR), and medical images 8.",
    "For example, Hu et al."
  ]
}